name: Mamory Balo
description: Im Mamory! I am extremely excited to see what this site can bring into my life. I do not have the best track record when it comes to dating, so I am a bit nervous. I look forward to hearing from you, beautiful ladies. Signing out, Mams xoxoxo

name: Elizabeth Foru
description: Any artists on here? I'm Lizzy! I love art, nature, and anything museum related. I am vegan and would love to meet someone who is as pro-saving the earth as I am. Would love to spend our days on this planet on a farm with many animals and five children.
